name: ROSARY TRUST (Rehabilitation of the socially afflicted, the retarded and the youth)
briefDescription: A Home for the aged, sheltering 100 neglected aged;  5 houses built for homeless families;  16 sewing machines given to poor young women;  90 poor students helped for 1 year education;  25 Women trained in tailoring;  18 free medical camps conducted in poor villages;  121 poor aged given winter clothing;  8 Cows gifted to destitute women;  2 toilets cum bathroom built for poor families; 6 Free Tuition centers are being run in 6 dalit village;  A Home for the handicapped, sheltering 50 neglected handicapped
